library(pacman)

p_load(data.table, viridis, tidyverse, ggrepel)

p_load_gh("hrbrmstr/hrbrthemes")

doc_theme <- theme_ipsum(
    base_family = "Arial", 
    caption_margin = 12,
    axis_title_size = 12,
    axis_col = "black")

interest <- fread("../../interest.tsv", sep = "\t")

aba.bed <- fread("../../CP046654.1.bed")

median_melted_results <- fread("../../Results/median_melted_results.tsv.gz")

median_melted_results[Pathway == "Other", Pathway := NA_character_]

median_melted_results[Pathway == "LPS", Pathway := "LOS"]

# https://version-11-5.string-db.org/cgi/globalenrichment?networkId=b1Fd534fBhzJ
CL707 <- fread ("../../CL707.tsv")
CL273 <- fread ("../../CL273.tsv")


median_melted_results %>% 
    filter(condition == "Imipenem_0.06_T1 - None_0_T1" & type == "perfect") %>% 
    mutate(
        Pathway = NA_character_,
        Pathway = case_when(
            AB030 %in% CL707$AB030 ~ "Cell Shape/Lipid Glyc.",
            AB030 %in% CL273$AB030 ~ "tRNA Aminoacylation"
        )) %>%
    
    arrange(AB19606) %>% 
    mutate(`Locus Tag Position` = factor(AB19606, levels = unique(AB19606))) %>% 
    mutate(`Locus Tag Position` = 1:n()) %>% 
    arrange(type) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = `Locus Tag Position`, y = medLFC)) +
    geom_hline(yintercept = 0,
        colour = "red",
        lty = "dashed") +
    geom_point(
        data = . %>% filter(is.na(Pathway)), 
        aes(fill = Pathway, size = -log10(FDR)),
        shape = 21,
        colour = "black",
        alpha = 0.5) + 
    geom_point(
        data = . %>% filter(!is.na(Pathway)), 
        aes(fill = Pathway, size = -log10(FDR)),
        shape = 21,
        colour = "black") + 
    doc_theme + 
    geom_label_repel(
        data = . %>% filter(Pathway %in% c("Cell Shape/Lipid Glyc.", "tRNA Aminoacylation")), 
        aes(label = gene_name_stylized), 
        parse = TRUE,
        max.overlaps = 25) + 
    scale_fill_viridis(
        discrete = T,
        alpha = 0.35,
        na.value = "grey", 
        direction = -1) +
    labs(
        title = bquote(bolditalic("Acinetobacter baumannii") ~ bold("Gene Sensitivity by Pathway")), 
        subtitle = bquote("Fitness defects beyond induction in Imipenem (0.09) at"~t[1]),
        parse = TRUE) +
    guides(
        size = "none",
        fill = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 10, alpha = 0.35))) -> p

print(p)

median_melted_results %>% 
    filter(condition == "Colistin_0.44_T2 - None_0_T2" & type == "perfect") %>% 
    arrange(AB19606) %>% 
    mutate(`Locus Tag Position` = factor(AB19606, levels = unique(AB19606))) %>% 
    mutate(`Locus Tag Position` = 1:n()) %>% 
    arrange(type) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = `Locus Tag Position`, y = medLFC)) +
    geom_hline(yintercept = 0,
        colour = "red",
        lty = "dashed") +
    geom_point(
        data = . %>% filter(is.na(Pathway)), 
        aes(fill = Pathway, size = -log10(FDR)),
        shape = 21,
        colour = "black",
        alpha = 0.5) + 
    geom_point(
        data = . %>% filter(!is.na(Pathway)), 
        aes(fill = Pathway, size = -log10(FDR)),
        shape = 21,
        colour = "black") + 
    doc_theme + 
    geom_label_repel(
        data = . %>% filter(Pathway %in% c("NADH", "LOS") & FDR < 0.05), 
        aes(label = gene_name_stylized), 
        parse = TRUE,
        max.overlaps = 25) + 
    scale_fill_viridis(
        discrete = T,
        alpha = 0.75,
        na.value = "grey", 
        direction = -1) +
    labs(
        title = bquote(bolditalic("Acinetobacter baumannii") ~ bold("Gene Sensitivity by Pathway")), 
        subtitle = "Fitness effects beyond induction in Colistin",
        parse = TRUE) +
    guides(
        size = "none",
        fill = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 10))) -> p

print(p)

median_melted_results %>% 
    inner_join(aba.bed %>% 
                            select(AB19606 = locus_tag, left, right)) %>%
    mutate(`Genome Coordinate` = (left + right)/2)    %>% 
    filter(
        (condition == "Colistin_0.44_T2 - None_0_T2" | condition == "Rifampicin_0.34_T2 - None_0_T2") & 
            type == "perfect") %>% 
    mutate(
        condition = case_when(
            condition == "Colistin_0.44_T2 - None_0_T2" ~ "Colistin at 18 hours",
            condition == "Rifampicin_0.34_T2 - None_0_T2" ~ "Rifampicin at 18 hours"),
        Pathway = case_when(
            unique_name %like% "rpo" ~ "RNAP",
            Pathway == "LOS" ~ "LOS",
            Pathway == "NADH" ~ "NADH"
        )) %>%
        arrange(`Genome Coordinate`) %>% 
    arrange(type) %>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = `Genome Coordinate`, y = medLFC)) +
    geom_hline(yintercept = 0,
               colour = "red",
               lty = "dashed") +
    geom_point(
        data = . %>% filter(is.na(Pathway)), 
        aes(fill = Pathway, size = -log10(FDR)),
        shape = 21,
        colour = "black",
        alpha = 0.2) + 
    geom_point(
        data = . %>% filter(!is.na(Pathway)), 
        aes(fill = Pathway, size = -log10(FDR)),
        shape = 21,
        colour = "black") + 
    doc_theme + 
    geom_label_repel(
        data = . %>% filter(
            Pathway %in% c("NADH", "LOS") |
                unique_name == "psd" |
                unique_name == "pssA" |
                unique_name == "cdsA" |
                unique_name == "rpoB"), 
        aes(label = gene_name_stylized), 
        parse = TRUE,
        max.overlaps = 50) + 
    scale_fill_viridis(
        discrete = T,
        alpha = 0.55,
        na.value = "grey", 
        direction = -1) +
    labs(
        title = bquote(bolditalic("Acinetobacter baumannii") ~ bold("Gene Sensitivity by Pathway")), 
        parse = TRUE) +
    guides(
        size = "none",
        fill = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size = 5))) + facet_wrap(facets = "condition") -> p
## Joining, by = "AB19606"
print(p)
